Interface IRectangle

ICefObjectWrapper, ICefObjRef, IComponentMouseDragEventObject, IComponentMouseEventObject, IEditableObject, IOptionedMapObject<MixedDataDictionary>, IVisibleMapObject

IRectangleWrapped
public interface IRectangle extends IVisibleMapObject, IEditableObject, IComponentMouseEventObject, IComponentMouseDragEventObject, IOptionedMapObject<MixedDataDictionary>
Represents an rectangle drawn on the map oriented along the latitude and longitude lines This corresponds to a Javascript Google Maps google.maps.Rectangle object
